{"Title":"白灼儿菜的做法","Primary":["儿菜1株"],"Auxiliary":["剁椒1茶匙","葱1段","清水1汤匙","水淀粉1茶匙","食盐1茶匙","植物油1汤匙","姜2片","蒜2瓣"],"Flavoring":[],"Setups":["1.把儿菜一个个掰下来，洗净","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/185/123/1655935/n1655935_142233488580937.jpg","2.每个剖成4瓣","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/185/123/1655935/n1655935_142233489392559.jpg","3.锅里水烧开，放入儿菜，少许盐，几滴油焯水2分钟捞出","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/185/123/1655935/n1655935_142233489827335.jpg","4.捞出的儿菜摆盘","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/185/123/1655935/n1655935_142233490796461.jpg","5.炒锅放少许油，放入葱、姜、蒜、剁椒小火煸香","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/185/123/1655935/n1655935_142233491835496.jpg","6.加少许水，盐煮开","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/185/123/1655935/n1655935_142233492534838.jpg","7.加水淀粉勾芡料汁就好了","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/185/123/1655935/n1655935_142233493702453.jpg","8.把料汁浇在菜上就可以吃啦，浓郁、清淡兼而有之","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/185/123/1655935/n1655935_142233494462570.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/185/123/1655935/n1655935_142233518126723.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/185/123/1655935/n1655935_142233518214450.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/185/123/1655935/n1655935_142233519258102.jpg"]}